<div class="full-post-footer "></div>
    </li>
            <li class="content-item">
        




<div class="full-post-header "></div>
<div class="full-post-container fiji-full-post-container evolution2-full-post-container"  data-reply-id="825512"  data-thread-starter="false" >
<div class="full-post ">
	<a name="825512"></a>
	<a name="825512"></a>
	<div class="post-author">
		<table class="post-author-details-table fiji-post-author-details-table evolution2-post-author-details-table" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0">
			<tr>
				<td class="post-author-avatar-cell fiji-post-author-avatar-cell evolution2-post-author-avatar-cell">
					<span class="avatar">
													<a href="/members/snowys-mum">
								<img src="/cfs-filesystemfile/__key/communityserver-components-imagefileviewer/communityserver-components-avatars-00-00-12-93-42/4TVVDZRIU4J3.jpg_2D00_32x32.jpg" border="0" alt="Snowys Mum" />
							</a>
											</span>
				</td>
				<td class="post-author-user-cell fiji-post-author-user-cell evolution2-post-author-user-cell">
				   <div class="user-name-post-date fiji-user-name-post-date evolution2-user-name-post-date">
						Posted by <span class="user-name">
															<a class="internal-link view-user-profile" href="/members/snowys-mum">
									<span></span>Snowys Mum
								</a>
													</span>
						<div class="post-date">
							<span class="label">
																	<a href="/cancer_types/breast-cancer/f/38/t/87484">on</a>
															</span>
							<span class="value"><a href='/cancer_types/breast-cancer/f/38/p/87484/825512#825512' class="internal-link view-post">2 Nov 2015 11:06 PM</a></span>
						</div>
																	</div>
				</td>
			</tr>
		</table>
	</div>
	
	
	<div class="post-content user-defined-markup">
					<p>Hi Everyone,</p>
<p>My Oncologist has stopped my Letrozole for 1 month when I showed her the results of the NHS predict tool which estimated the benefit of me taking it was 0.3% at five years and 0.7% at 10 years.</p>
<p>The tool shows your chances of being alive in 5 and 10 years as compared to the general population and the increase that the hormone inhibitor gives you.</p>
<p>I am seeing her again on 24th Nov so she may recommend I start it again, but all those SE&#39;s for 0.7% :(</p><div style="clear:both;"></div>
					</div>

	



	  

<div class="fiji-post-details-container-outer evolution2-post-details-container-outer">
